    Instrumentable, Extractor<S,RecordEnvelope<D>>, StreamingExtractor<S,D>, FinalState, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class KafkaSimpleStreamingExtractor<S,D>
extends EventBasedExtractor<S,RecordEnvelope<D>>
implements StreamingExtractor<S,D>
    An implementation of StreamingExtractor which reads from Kafka and returns records . Type of record depends on deserializer set.
